---
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
---
<section class="cta-section">
  <div class="container cta-section__inner">
    <p class="cta-section__lead">まずはお気軽にご相談ください</p>
    <p class="cta-section__sub">公共工事から個人住宅のリフォームまで、どんなご相談にも対応いたします。</p>
    <div class="cta-section__actions">
      <a href="tel:0115111951" class="cta-section__tel">
        <span class="cta-section__tel-label">お電話でのお問い合わせ</span>
        <span class="cta-section__tel-num">011-511-1951</span>
      </a>
      <a href={`${base}contact/`} class="btn btn--gold cta-section__btn">メールで問い合わせる</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .cta-section {
    background: var(--c-navy);
    padding: var(--sp-3xl) 0;
    text-align: center;
    color: var(--c-white);
  }
  .cta-section__lead {
    font-family: var(--ff-serif);
    font-size: var(--fs-h2);
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: var(--sp-sm);
  }
  .cta-section__sub {
    font-size: var(--fs-body);
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
    margin-bottom: var(--sp-lg);
  }
  .cta-section__actions {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: var(--sp-lg);
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .cta-section__tel {
    text-align: center;
  }
  .cta-section__tel-label {
    display: block;
    font-size: var(--fs-small);
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6);
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }
  .cta-section__tel-num {
    font-family: var(--ff-condensed);
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  }
  .cta-section__btn {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    padding: 16px 40px;
  }
</style>
